Detailed Description

template<template< size_t > class ValueType = IntervalSemantics::ValueType>
class BinaryAnalysis::InstructionSemantics::IntervalSemantics::MemoryCell< ValueType >

Memory cell with interval address and data.

The ValueType template argument should be a subclass of IntervalSemantics::ValueType.
